<header class="admin-header">
  <div>
    <h1 class="admin-title">데이터 Import</h1>
    <p class="admin-subtitle">엑셀 파일로 문항과 채점 정의를 일괄 등록하세요</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="admin-card">
  <h2>Import 실행 방법</h2>
  <p class="admin-muted">서버에서 아래 명령으로 Import를 실행하세요.</p>
  <pre><code>bundle exec rails runner script/import_literacy_bank.rb path/to/file.xlsx --dry-run</code></pre>
  <pre><code>bundle exec rails runner script/import_literacy_bank.rb path/to/file.xlsx</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="admin-card">
  <h2>현재 데이터 상태</h2>
  <table class="admin-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>항목</th>
        <th>수량</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>문항</td>
        <td><%= @items_count %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>객관식 보기</td>
        <td><%= @choices_count %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>루브릭</td>
        <td><%= @rubrics_count %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>최근 문항 생성</td>
        <td><%= @last_item_at&.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M") || "-" %></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>
